text: Meghan Marguerite McCain (born October 23, 1984) is an American columnist, author, former Fox News contributor, and former co-host of The View. She is the daughter of diplomat Cindy McCain and the late senator John McCain. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:American columnists Category:American television presenters Category:American political commentators Category:Republicans (United States) Category:Fox News people Category:Writers from Phoenix, Arizona Category:Entertainers from Phoenix, Arizona
